<p><strong><em>Incorporeal Movement.</em></strong> The avatar can move through other creatures and objects as if they were difficult terrain. It takes 5 (1d10) force damage if it ends its turn inside an object.</p>

<p><strong><em>Turning Immunity.</em></strong> The avatar is immune to features that turn undead.</p>

<p><strong><em>Hit Points.</em></strong> The Avatar of Death appears with hit points equal to half its summonerâ€™s maximum hit points.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Reaping Scythe.</em></strong> The avatar sweeps its spectral scythe through a creature within 5 feet of it, dealing 7 (1d8 + 3) slashing damage plus 4 (1d8) necrotic damage.</p>

